features: Fairy Princess Activity Pack is ideal for children aged 3-8 years. Contains 2 Fairy Princess Colouring books, 1 Fairy Princess Sticker book, 3 Sheets with over 100 reusable stickers, a stationery set and a set of 6 mini colouring pencils.
Both Fairy Princess Colouring books contain 8 pages (16 sides). The dimensions of the books are 220 x 175mm.

Fairy Princess Sticker book contains 6 pages (12 sides) and a double page of stickers. The dimensions of the book is 260 x 205mm. You'll have 100 reusable stickers included on the sheets that you can place them wherever you choose, whether its in the sticker book or to decorate your own work!
The Princess stationery set includes a pencil, ruler, rubber and a sharpener. Colours included in the mini colouring pencils are pink, blue, green, yellow, orange and red.
Handy carry along case with handle, perfect for travel and car journeys. The colouring books are filled with colouring & activities for keeping children entertained for hours.
